Package: ptools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for compact programming
Version: 0.01
Date: 2012-09-21
Author: Peter Meilstrup <peter.meilstrup@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Peter Meilstrup <peter.meilstrup@gmail.com>
Description: Functions for expressing ideas while saving
    keystrokes. There is a function for creating pipelines, a
    destructuring bind, a function for creating functions, a function
    for indexing data frames, and (soon) functions for fast
    split-apply-combine operations on data frames.
License: MIT
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 0.2)
Imports:
    plyr (>= 1.7.0)
Collate:
    'chain.R'
    'indexing.R'
    'programming.R'
    'ptools-description.R'
    'fun.R'
    'bind.R'
    'macro.R'
    'resources.R'
    'run_as_script.R'
    'with_args.R'
    'ammoc.R'
    'getPointer.R'
